text: Novaya Uralka () is a rural locality (a village) in Otradinsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 232 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 3 km from Yermolayevo, 12 km from Staraya Otrada. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Novaya Uralka
